# The bare data/ rule above targets this repo's own runtime photo storage
# (./data/media/photos); it's unanchored, so it also matches
# frontend/src/data/ — committed source data (copies of the eval/ benchmark
# JSONs for the Glass box page, see frontend/src/components/GlassBoxTab.tsx)
# that must be tracked. Un-ignore it explicitly.
!frontend/src/data/

